title: GitHub Actions
description: Search pinned GitHub Actions versions, copy ready-to-use uses lines, and install gh-pin to pin workflows locally.
tab: github-actions
---

<section aria-labelledby="tool-title" class="tool-intro">
	<div class="panel-heading">
		<h1 id="tool-title">GitHub Actions</h1>
		<p class="panel-copy">
			Install <a href="https://github.com/unfunco/gh-pin"><code>gh-pin</code></a> to pin workflow actions locally before you commit. It uses the same shared pin list as this site and helps replace mutable tags with immutable SHAs.
		</p>
	</div>
	<pre class="command-block"><code class="language-bash">gh extension install unfunco/gh-pin
gh pin</code></pre>
</section>

<section aria-labelledby="search-title" class="search-panel" id="search-panel">
	<div class="panel-heading">
		<h2 id="search-title">Search pinned actions</h2>
		<p class="panel-copy">Search the shared pin list and copy ready-to-use <code>uses:</code> lines.</p>
	</div>
	<div class="search-box">
		<label class="search-label" for="search">Action name</label>
		<input
			autocapitalize="off"
			autocomplete="off"
			autocorrect="off"
			id="search"
			name="search"
			placeholder="Search GitHub Actions..."
			spellcheck="false"
			type="text"
		>
		<p class="search-status" id="search-status" role="status">
			Loading pinned actions...
		</p>
	</div>
	<div aria-live="polite" class="results" id="results"></div>
	<noscript>
		<p class="noscript">JavaScript is required to search and copy pins on this page.</p>
	</noscript>
</section>
